to resource ros packages:

    source ~/MowerRobot/devel/setup.bash


to ssh to Pi

ssh tlia@ICEcreamPi.local


To run program:
run following command on both machine
    export ROS_MASTER_URI=http://ICEcreamPi.local:11311
    
than on viewer:
    rosrun rviz rviz -d "/home/tlia/MowerRobot/src/mowerRobot/mowerRobot_Launch/rviz/mower.rviz"

on pi:
    export ROS_IP=ICEcreamPi.local
    roslaunch mowerRobot_launch mowerRobot.launch
